high_descs: Turn around and walk five steps, turn left for two steps, turn right and walk to the table top by the wall straight ahead.
Pick up the blue circular item.
Turn right for five steps, turn right for one step, take a left for three steps, turn right for one step and face the coffee table.
Put the blue item on the coffee table in front of the keys near the edge.
Turn right and walk until you reach the wall, turn tight and over to the table by the wall.
Pick up the glass vase.from the top left of the table.
Turn right for seven steps, turn right for one steps, turn left for three steps and turn right for one step to face the coffee table.
Put the vase on the coffee table directly down from the white square plate on the table but closer to the edge.
anns.task_desc: Put a vase and a blue round item on the coffee table.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the low black shelf across the room.
Pick up the blue vase from the shelf.
Turn around and walk to the glass coffee table.
Put the blue vase on the table to the right of the green statue.
Turn right and take a right at the wall to face the low black shelf.
Pick up the glass vase from the shelf.
Turn around and walk to the glass coffee table.
Place the glass vase to the left of the green statue on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place two vases on a table.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the gray dresser across the room.
Pick up the blue bottle on the dresser.
Turn right and go to the side of the coffee table facing the wall.
Place the blue bottle in front of the keys on the table.
Turn right and go back to the gray dresser on the right.
Pick up the glass jar on the dresser towards the back.
Turn right and go back to the coffee table on the right.
Place the glass jar on the table on the left of the blue bottle.
anns.task_desc: Move the blue bottle and glass jar from the dresser to the coffee table.
